{"tid":2512572,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–脂肪細胞與糖份","createTime":"2021-05-01T22:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T07:19:49.000Z","uid":38861,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"518bc9f53126853314ee5be04c345cc1b618a6b7","tid":2512572,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:31:54.000Z","msg":"進食含有糖份的食物後，血液胰島素濃度便會上升，輔助細胞們吸取葡萄糖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZXMrEweLhQVDAz4WjG38mdoNBN82gM84Ur8XC82x4y1H?filename=DUykZZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUykZZ1.jpg&h=d3356cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在利用肌肉細胞及脂肪細胞的實驗中，胰島素錄得可以在數分鐘內增強細胞的吸收葡萄糖效率2-10倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)細胞需要特定位於表面的蛋白質幫忙，才能有效吸取糖份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaKGpg6X95huzi66kcBxq4VYvr6SMCkzFgAGizvRfL43d?filename=1rVjv6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rVjv6J.jpg&h=c6d37b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGLUT4是其中一款負責吸取糖份的蛋白質，但它平常所在的位置是在細部內部、而非位於表面。<br />\n當細胞遇上胰島素的時候，GLUT4就會轉移到細胞表面，加快細胞吸收糖份的效率。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)肌肉細胞及脂肪細胞均擁有GLUT4蛋白質，因此胰島素能增強它們吸取糖份的效率。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXPJ13goo9XpoJdsjfCshpxN12TnRTWmgh1apmW69x4od?filename=vXPXhMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXPXhMM.jpg&h=b5e9b9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但兩者不同的是，肌肉會將過量的糖份轉化成為糖原(Glycogen)，<br />\n<br />\n而脂肪細胞僅會將過量糖份的5%左右轉化成為糖原，另外的50%轉化成為脂肪(Triglyceride)，其餘的則不會用作儲存。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，餐後的葡萄糖，僅約20%會被脂肪細胞所吸收，另外80%均由其他細胞使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=dd1c41fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=99180082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell-metabolism/fulltext/S1550-4131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell-metabolism%2Ffulltext%2FS1550-4131&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=1473d317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell-metabolism/fulltext/S1550-4131</a>(21)00126-1#fig1"},{"pid":"4a1e0d64cdc08b97c0330184bc2be8401e6ddff7","tid":2512572,"uid":109560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:55:49.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e60608ba0b52174bc4314c82d6adf3147b4128","tid":2512572,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:57:59.000Z","msg":"淨係食粥／純澱粉<br />\n隔一陣之後feel到血糖急跌頭暈漂冷汗<br />\n係咪身體有問題"},{"pid":"2ff7a0c882370fe2ff8016c3d601365289affc95","tid":2512572,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:58:15.000Z","msg":"sor 慣咗手勢不推"},{"pid":"c316e3fe3614a25b58a09a83ad0ac9e38bd77170","tid":2512572,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,