0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e60608ba0b52174bc4314c82d6adf3147b4128","tid":2512572,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:57:59.000Z","msg":"淨係食粥／純澱粉<br />\n隔一陣之後feel到血糖急跌頭暈漂冷汗<br />\n係咪身體有問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:01:55.000Z","msg":"食粥都跌血糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生好喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />胰島素分泌問題？"},{"pid":"8a7615ae9d891b60ceece273b37f0cc58de988ed","tid":2512572,"uid":309049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:32:38.000Z","msg":"睇完，有d複雜，咁結論係咩？係味要做多d運動增加肌肉量？"},{"pid":"a96638953ee22a5d4c8465be1a9be2d4f12f10c0","tid":2512572,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"62e60608ba0b52174bc4314c82d6adf3147b4128","tid":2512572,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:57:59.000Z","msg":"淨係食粥／純澱粉<br />\n隔一陣之後feel到血糖急跌頭暈漂冷汗<br />\n係咪身體有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:45:00.000Z","msg":"tldr: 有可能係你insulin 分泌過多，建議你可以記錄底病發時間同埋test 血糖去confirm<br />\n<br />\nReactive hypoglycemia (postprandial hypoglycemia) refers to low blood sugar that occurs after a meal &mdash; usually within four hours after eating. This is different from low blood sugar (hypoglycemia) that occurs while fasting.<br />\n<br />\n When the first-phase insulin response decreases, firstly, blood glucose starts to rise after the meal. This leads to late but excessive secretion of the second-phase insulin secretion. Thus, late reactive hypoglycemia occurs."},{"pid":"b2493c58989b991c754a596ed733968912e693ce","tid":2512572,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a7615ae9d891b60ceece273b37f0cc58de988ed","tid":2512572,"uid":309049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:32:38.000Z","msg":"睇完，有d複雜，咁結論係咩？係味要做多d運動增加肌肉量？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:58:14.000Z","msg":"後天糖尿基本上係insulin resistance, 啲細胞對胰島素無反應。<br />\n<br />\nInsulin resistance is a feature of a number of clinical disorders, including type 2 diabetes/glucose intolerance, obesity, dyslipidaemia and hypertension clustering in the so-called metabolic syndrome. Insulin resistance in skeletal muscle manifests itself primarily as a reduction in insulin-stimulated glycogen synthesis due to reduced glucose transport. Ectopic lipid accumulation plays an important role in inducing insulin resistance. Multiple defects in insulin signalling are responsible for impaired glucose metabolism in target tissues of subjects with features of insulin resistance. <span class=\"red\">Inflammatory molecules and lipid metabolites inhibit insulin signalling </span>by stimulating a number of different serine kinases which are responsible for serine phosphorylation of Insulin Receptor Substrate-1 (IRS-1).<br />\n<br />\n下列係會增加resistance 風險嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\noverweight or obesity (過多脂肪會防礙細胞同胰島素之間嘅作用，減少糖份吸收）<br />\nage 45 or older (人老咗身體機能自然下降）<br />\na parent, brother, or sister with diabetes (基因）<br />\nAfrican American, Alaska Native, American Indian, Asian American, Hispanic/Latino, Native Hawaiian, or Pacific Islander American ethnicity (基因）<br />\nphysical inactivity (同痴肥同埋）<br />\nhealth conditions such as high blood pressure and abnormal cholesterol levels (同痴肥同埋，再加上心臟病係associated with 發炎，而發炎會進一步影響細胞對血糖嘅利用）<br />\na history of heart disease or stroke (同上）<br />\na history of gestational diabetes (唔清楚）<br />\npolycystic ovary syndrome, also called PCOS (懶得查）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1521690X06000789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1521690X06000789&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=0064ada8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1521690X06000789</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/diabetes/overview/what-is-diabetes/prediabetes-insulin-resistance#insulinresistance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niddk.nih.gov%2Fhealth-information%2Fdiabetes%2Foverview%2Fwhat-is-diabetes%2Fprediabetes-insulin-resistance%23insulinresistance&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=1f59ce04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/diabetes/overview/what-is-diabetes/prediabetes-insulin-resistance#insulinresistance</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hindawi.com/journals/bmri/2014/406960/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindawi.com%2Fjournals%2Fbmri%2F2014%2F406960%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=9c2419c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hindawi.com/journals/bmri/2014/406960/</a>"},{"pid":"34602dcb74aa045e4126096aef3024539b115d73","tid":2512572,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T00:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08553eca02b39f36994e1b4c2518e2e3c2777c0d","tid":2512572,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45c9ee96f562de5c2541bebe3ea64d05ac19a690","tid":2512572,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e28afae019c823b436a688c40eee341331009c54","tid":2512572,"uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e60608ba0b52174bc4314c82d6adf3147b4128","tid":2512572,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:57:59.000Z","msg":"淨係食粥／純澱粉<br />\n隔一陣之後feel到血糖急跌頭暈漂冷汗<br />\n係咪身體有問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:01:55.000Z","msg":"食粥都跌血糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生好喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />胰島素分泌問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:07:52.000Z","msg":"粥嘅升糖指數高㗎, 高過飯<br />\n會唔會係你食完粥, 血糖颷升, 但細胞唔識吸收糖份, 於是胰臟釋放更多胰島素, 然後你血糖過低, 出現低血糖癥狀?<br />\n所以或者你有糖尿病傾向? <br />\n最好都係去check, 早發現早控制好重要<br />\n利申: 乜都唔識, 唔知講得啱唔岩"},{"pid":"cbea4e5d0c04724be8a7ff1261e96878c3210fe1","tid":2512572,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"有時午餐食得唔夠多，夜晚六點個人會無力，有d標汗係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b0826819023bd07f7563b5b880bacdb79c725a","tid":2512572,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"轉成糖源係好定唔好"},{"pid":"160574b8024f7989095ee9d7fabc8eb15167beef","tid":2512572,"uid":303464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"咁肌肉將多餘嘅轉做糖原，糖原又有咩用？"},{"pid":"7d5053d25266135e61abf9d8d9eb55dbb0913968","tid":2512572,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"你讀UoH?"},{"pid":"98a065017f6c3f3e9b85247556118f3472a0abec","tid":2512572,"uid":243761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"160574b8024f7989095ee9d7fabc8eb15167beef","tid":2512572,"uid":303464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"咁肌肉將多餘嘅轉做糖原，糖原又有咩用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"第時有需要用會再拎返出黎轉做糖用"}]}